description: US, 1942, from blow off (“to fellate”, originating among prostitutes from 1933) +‎ job.

entries.meaning: (sex, vulgar) An act of fellatio, or sucking a penis or other phallic object (such as a dildo). Stimulation of somebody's penis or testicles with a person's lips, tongue or mouth with the purpose of giving the receiver sexual pleasure. It may or may not result in orgasm.

examples: You just don't hear much about it because no foreign nation is going to complain when a US president wants to give them a collective blowjob.
